<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-+0n0xVW2eSR5OomGNYDnhzAbDsOXxcvSN1TPprVMTNDbiYZCxYbOOl7+AMvyTG2x" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <script src="fontawesome.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Universus - Universal Media Downloader</title>
  </head>
  <body style="min-height: 100vh;">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light sticky-top">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
          <img src="universus_logo.png" alt="" width="35" height="35" />
        </a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarScroll" aria-controls="navbarScroll" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarScroll">
          <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto my-2 my-lg-0 navbar-nav-scroll" style="--bs-scroll-height: 100px;">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#download">Download</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="#q&a">Q&A</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="navbar-nav d-flex flex-row me-2 d-lg-inline d-none">
        <li class="nav-item me-2">
          <a class="nav-link" style="font-size: 25px;" href="https://github.com/willuhm-js/Universus" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <div class="container text-center p-5" style="font-size: 47px;">
      <img src="workswith.png" width="230px" height="50px" />
      <br />
      <i style="color: #ff0000;" class="fab fa-youtube m-1"></i>
      <i style="color: #1ed760;" class="fab fa-spotify m-1"></i>
      <i style="color: #e1306c;" class="fab fa-instagram m-1"></i>
      <i style="color: #4267b2;" class="fab fa-facebook m-1"></i>
      <i style="color: #1da1f2;" class="fab fa-twitter m-1"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid bg-dark p-4" id="download">
      <div class="container p-5">
        <br />
        <form class="row align-items-center" method="POST" action="/preview">
          <%- brTag %>
          <div class="col-8">
            <div class="input-group">
              <input autocomplete="off" id="link_input" type="url" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ" name="link" required />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-4">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-light btn-lg">Download</button>
          </div>
          <%- textElement %>
        </form>
        <br />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container ms-5 mt-5 p-1" id="q&a">
    <h3>Commonly Asked Questions</h3>
    <br>
      <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#question1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question1" style="cursor: pointer;">
        <p>What does Universus do?</p>
        <hr style="width: 80vw;" />
      </div>
      <div class="collapse" id="question1">
        <div class="mb-1">
          Universus is a media downloader that allows you to download photo/video/audio from a variety of social media platforms.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="containe ms-5 mt-1 p-1">
      <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#question2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question2" style="cursor: pointer;">
        <p>What platforms does Universus support?</p>
        <hr style="width: 80vw;" />
      </div>
      <div class="collapse" id="question2">
        <div>
          <p>Universus currently supports YouTube, Spotify, Instagram, Facebook, and Twitter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="containe ms-5 mt-1 p-1">
      <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#question3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="question3" style="cursor: pointer;">
        <p>Is Universus open source?</p>
        <hr style="width: 80vw;" />
      </div>
      <div class="collapse" id="question3">
        <div class="mb-2">
          <p>Yup! Find the code for this project <a href="https://github.com/willuhm-js/Universus" target="_blank">here</a>!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <footer class="p-1 text-center">
      <p style="color: 333333;">MIT License | William Faircloth</p>
    </footer>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-gtEjrD/SeCtmISkJkNUaaKMoLD0//ElJ19smozuHV6z3Iehds+3Ulb9Bn9Plx0x4" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="placeholder.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
